<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>TheResumes.Online - Welcome User</title>
  </head>
  <body
    style="
      background: #f3f3f3;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
    "
  >
    <div
      style="
        width: auto;
        max-width: 500px;
        margin: 20px auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background: #fffef9;
      "
    >
      <a
        href="https://theresumes.online"
        style="
          display: block;
          width: auto;
          max-width: 200px;
          overflow: hidden;
          margin: 0 auto 20px;
        "
      >
        <img
          src="https://theresumes.online/src/static/emailer/logo.png"
          alt="TheResumes.Online"
          style="
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            object-position: center;
            object-fit: contain;
          "
        />
      </a>

      <div style="background: #f3f3f3">
        <div class="image" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; overflow: hidden">
          <img
            src="https://theresumes.online/src/static/emailer/banners/01.jpg"
            alt=""
            style="width: 100%; height: 100%"
          />
        </div>
        <div style="padding: 15px">
          <p
            style="
              font-size: 14px;
              font-weight: 400;
              color: #333333;
              margin-bottom: 10px;
            "
          >
            <b>Dear <%= name %>,</b>
          </p>
          <p
            style="
              font-size: 14px;
              font-weight: 400;
              color: #666666;
              margin-bottom: 10px;
            "
          >
            Welcome to TheResumes.online, your gateway to crafting standout
            resumes that get you noticed in today's competitive job market!
          </p>
          <p
            style="
              font-size: 14px;
              font-weight: 400;
              color: #666666;
              margin-bottom: 10px;
            "
          >
            Get ready to unlock your career potential with our user-friendly
            platform with customizable templates and expert tips. Whether you're
            aiming for a promotion, switching industries, or just want to polish
            your profile, we've got everything you need to make a lasting
            impression.
          </p>
          <p
            style="
              font-size: 14px;
              font-weight: 400;
              color: #666666;
              margin-bottom: 10px;
            "
          >
            <b>
              <u>Here's what's in store for you:</u>
            </b>
          </p>
          <ol style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding-left: 10px">
            <li style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: #666666">
              <b>Tailored Templates, Tailored Success:</b> Choose from various
              eye-catching templates designed to showcase your skills and
              experience.
            </li>
            <li style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: #666666">
              <b>User-friendly Interface:</b> Our platform is designed to be
              intuitive and easy to navigate, ensuring you have a seamless
              experience while building your resume.
            </li>
            <li style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: #666666">
              <b>24/7 Support:</b> Need help? Our dedicated support team is here
              round the clock to assist you on your journey to career greatness.
            </li>
          </ol>
          <p
            style="
              font-size: 14px;
              font-weight: 400;
              color: #666666;
              margin-bottom: 10px;
            "
          >
            Don't wait - login now at
            <a href="https://theresumes.online/login" target="_blank"
              >https://theresumes.online/login</a
            >
            to start building the resume that opens doors to your dream job.
          </p>
          <p
            style="
              font-size: 14px;
              font-weight: 400;
              color: #666666;
              margin-bottom: 10px;
            "
          >
            Let's build your future together! <br />
            Best regards,
          </p>
          <p
            style="
              font-size: 14px;
              font-weight: 400;
              color: #666666;
              margin-bottom: 10px;
            "
          >
            Customer Success Team <br />TheResumes.online
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-top: 30px; text-align: center">
        <div style="margin: 0 auto 30px; text-align: center">
          <a
            href="https://www.facebook.com/theresumes.online"
            target="_blank"
            style="text-decoration: none; margin: 0 3px"
          >
            <img
              src="https://theresumes.online/src/static/emailer/social/fb.png"
              style="width: 40px"
            />
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://www.instagram.com/theresumes.online/"
            target="_blank"
            style="text-decoration: none; margin: 0 3px"
          >
            <img
              src="https://theresumes.online/src/static/emailer/social/ig.png"
              style="width: 40px; margin: 0 3px"
            />
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://x.com/the_resumes"
            target="_blank"
            style="text-decoration: none; margin: 0 3px"
          >
            <img
              src="https://theresumes.online/src/static/emailer/social/x.png"
              style="width: 40px"
            />
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://www.linkedin.com/showcase/theresumes/about/"
            target="_blank"
            style="text-decoration: none; margin: 0 3px"
          >
            <img
              src="https://theresumes.online/src/static/emailer/social/in.png"
              style="width: 40px"
            />
          </a>
        </div>

        <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #666666">
          To make sure you continue receiving our newsletters, add
          <a
            href="mailto:newsletter@theresumes.online"
            style="text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; color: #333333"
            >newsletter&#64;theresumes.online</a
          >
          to your address book.
        </p>

        <p style="font-size: 10px; color: #666666">
          <a
            href="https://theresumes.online/unsubscribe/<%= encodeURIComponent(_id) %>"
            style="text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; color: #333333"
            >Unsubscribe</a
          >
        </p>

        <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #666666">
          <a
            href="https://theresumes.online"
            style="text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; color: #333333"
            >theresumes.online</a
          >
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
